Step 1: Create Project Folder
Objective

Create the project directory that will contain all application files.

Folder Name
AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
Create Folder
Windows
mkdir AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
cd AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
Linux / Chromebook
mkdir AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
cd AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
Verify Current Directory
pwd

Example Output

/home/sugumar/AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
Create Initial Structure
mkdir templates
mkdir static
mkdir static/css
mkdir static/js
mkdir static/images
touch app.py
Your Folder Should Look Like
AI_Employee_Salary_Predictor
│
├── app.py
│
├── templates
│
└── static
    ├── css
    ├── images
    └── js
Verify Folder Structure

Linux

tree

If tree is not installed:

ls -R

